room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 12" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
review: This escape room is terrific - realistic, challenging, immersive, great use of details and decorations and super fun. I think out of all the ones I've ever done, this is my favorite just for the atmosphere in the jail cells and how fun it is to escape. Highly recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 12" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
review: Very challenging Escape Rooms, the design of these games are excellent for groups of 4-8. Hats off to the detail in construction and concept. Bring your A game to get out in time. Good luck!

room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 12" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
review: This was so much fun! I recommend everyone find a group of friends and try a room! We have never worked so well together and laughed so much! Great night out for everyone!

room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 12" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
review: Its the 10th room I've done, and we all had a blast! Really great people putting a great Escape game together.We all can't wait to try their other one.
